{"title":"linux_CentOS7_yum时出错，Could not retrieve mirrorlist","date":"2018-08-05T05:38:00.000Z","link":"post/176","categories":["Liunx"],"updated":"2019-06-23T14:31:53.865Z","content":"<h4 id=\"错误如下：\">错误如下：<a href=\"post/176#错误如下：\"></a></h4><p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/3219025162.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"解决方法：\">解决方法：<a href=\"post/176#解决方法：\"></a></h4><p> 错误原因：  <strong>没有配置/etc/resolv.conf</strong><br> 解决方法：<br> <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vi /etc/resolv.conf</span><br><span class=\"line\">//添加</span><br><span class=\"line\">nameserver 8.8.8.8</span><br><span class=\"line\">search localdomain</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/3500862839.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Centos7上卸载MariaDB数据库和本地Navicat连接不上虚拟机数据库","link":"post/178"},"next":{"title":" JQuery点击事件回到页面顶部效果","link":"post/172"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/176/"}